data.title: The Duke and Duchess of Connaught with their children and Gustaf Adolf, Crown Prince of Sweden
data.meta_description: Photograph of a group portrait of Prince Arthur, Duke of Connaught with his wife, Princess Louise Margaret of Prussia, and their children, Princess Patricia of Connaught, Prince Arthur of Connaught and Princess Margaret of Connaught, and Princess Margarets husband, Gustaf Adolf, Crown Prince of Sweden. The Duke and Duchess of Connaught are seated in chairs in the foreground, on the left. The group are dressed for the Coronation of King George V and Queen Mary. Prince Gustaf Adolf wears the...
